title: Bug 114903: Default values are not shown in 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
OB: When accessing the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the parameters are not displayed.
EB: The 'Show Report Parameters' dialog should display the default values for the parameters.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:1. Open the application.2. Navigate to the reports section.3. Select a report that requires parameters.4. Click on the 'Show Report Parameters' button.5. Observe that the default values for the parameters are not shown in the dialog.
